271
00:17:58,310 --> 00:18:00,610
I'll come back to see you soon.

272
00:18:09,920 --> 00:18:11,470
Hello?

273
00:18:11,470 --> 00:18:12,880
Loan?

274
00:18:12,880 --> 00:18:14,390
