345
00:21:41,820 --> 00:21:43,200
Don't worry.

346
00:21:43,200 --> 00:21:47,280
After Xuan Xuan has her surgery, I'll have Grandpa lined up for another spot.

347
00:21:51,540 --> 00:21:56,320
